metadata.name: SARI
metadata.description:
Sari: the goddess of forests and woods, the protector of the Earth made of sunsets and moon soil.. Sari's teardrops water all living organisms, protect flocks of cattle, howl with wolves, immerse into roots of the sorrow and promote life and fertility... Sari is a fierce soul, feminine and masculine .. she is not afraid of conquering mountains.. she starts the day with conquering herself....

4000 x 4000 px 600 DPI  
Ani Mkhitaryan, 2022
